com.informatica.mdm.bpm.interfaces.data

Interface ITaskData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IDDTaskData

    public interface ITaskData
    Represents the task data. This is used to pass task related data for the various methods of IBPMAdapter and IBPMProcessGenerator. This also has place holders for any records associated with the task.

    IDDTaskData, the IDD specific implementation of this interface, is included in the SDK.

    See Also:
    IDDTaskData
